#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.12:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Rathakāravagga"
msgstr "2. The Chariot-maker"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Sāraṇīyasutta"
msgstr "12. Commemoration"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: sāraṇīyāni → sārāṇīyāni (bj) | saraṇīyāni (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.12:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, rañño khattiyassa muddhāvasittassa yāvajīvaṃ "
"sāraṇīyāni bhavanti."
msgstr "“An anointed king should commemorate three places as long as he lives."

msgctxt "an3.12:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.12:1.3"
msgid "Yasmiṃ, bhikkhave, padese rājā khattiyo muddhāvasitto jāto hoti."
msgstr "The place he was born."

msgctxt "an3.12:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamaṃ rañño khattiyassa muddhāvasittassa yāvajīvaṃ "
"sāraṇīyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is the first place."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.12:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ padese rājā khattiyo muddhāvasitto hoti."
msgstr "The place he was anointed as king."

msgctxt "an3.12:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyaṃ rañño khattiyassa muddhāvasittassa yāvajīvaṃ "
"sāraṇīyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is the second place."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.12:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ padese rājā khattiyo muddhāvasitto saṅgāmaṃ "
"abhivijinitvā vijitasaṅgāmo tameva saṅgāmasīsaṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""
"The place where he won victory in battle, establishing himself as foremost "
"in battle."

msgctxt "an3.12:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyaṃ rañño khattiyassa muddhāvasittassa yāvajīvaṃ "
"sāraṇīyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is the third place."

msgctxt "an3.12:3.3"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi rañño khattiyassa muddhāvasittassa yāvajīvaṃ "
"sāraṇīyāni bhavanti."
msgstr ""
"These are the three places an anointed king should commemorate as long as he "
"lives."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.107"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.12:4.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tīṇimāni bhikkhussa yāvajīvaṃ sāraṇīyāni bhavanti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant should commemorate three places as long as they "
"live."

msgctxt "an3.12:4.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.12:4.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, bhikkhave, padese bhikkhu kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni "
"acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti."
msgstr ""
"The place where the mendicant shaved off their hair and beard, dressed in "
"ocher robes, and went forth from the lay life to homelessness."

msgctxt "an3.12:4.4"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamaṃ bhikkhussa yāvajīvaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is the first place."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.12:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ padese bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’"
"ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"The place where the mendicant truly understands: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This "
"is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This "
"is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an3.12:5.2"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyaṃ bhikkhussa yāvajīvaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is the second place."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.12:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ padese bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ "
"cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"The place where the mendicant realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and "
"freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live having realized it with "
"their own insight due to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an3.12:6.2"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyaṃ bhikkhussa yāvajīvaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is the third place."

msgctxt "an3.12:6.3"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi bhikkhussa yāvajīvaṃ sāraṇīyāni bhavantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the three places a mendicant should commemorate as long as they "
"live.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.12:6.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
